<p>Rescuing our dog from the shelter changed our lives in ways we never expected. From the moment we met them, we could feel how much love and care had gone into protecting them and helping them heal. The shelter gave our dog safety, patience, and kindness when they needed it most, and because of that, they were able to trust again. Watching our Si blossom in our home has been nothing short of a miracle. We are forever grateful for the compassion, dedication, and heart behind this rescue.</p>
